</div></div><div class="widget__head">
                        
                        <div class="widget__image crop-3x2"
                                        role="img"
                                        aria-label="Massachusetts Schoolchildren Saw Goody Johnson ... Wait, No, They&#39;re Calling For Her Pardon"
                                            
                                        style="background-image: url('https://assets.rebelmouse.io/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNzI3NzU2NC9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY4ODAyNzMwMH0.by6oNry78U6eTO-vVTcLZHbk1n0O7y7B9bHOvLXS_JE/img.jpg?width=1200&quality=85&coordinates=0%2C0%2C0%2C35&height=800'); padding-bottom: 66.6666666667%; "
                                                
                                            
                                        style='background-image: url("https://assets.rebelmouse.io/eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpbWFnZSI6Imh0dHBzOi8vYXNzZXRzLnJibC5tcy8yNzI3NzU2NC9vcmlnaW4uanBnIiwiZXhwaXJlc19hdCI6MTY4ODAyNzMwMH0.by6oNry78U6eTO-vVTcLZHbk1n0O7y7B9bHOvLXS_JE/img.jpg?width=1200&quality=85&coordinates=0%2C0%2C0%2C35&height=800"); padding-bottom: 66.6666666667%;'data-type="image"
                                ><div class="lazyload-placeholder">
                                        <div class="runner-spinner">
                                        <svg class="runner-spinner-circular" viewBox="25 25 50 50">
                                            <circle class="runner-spinner-path" cx="50" cy="50" r="20" fill="none" stroke-width="3" stroke-miterlimit="10"/>
